  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Radiofrequency emmitting device, normaly used for thermage treatments will be used on 22
      mild to moderate acne patients faces.

      The aim of the study is to check whether RF heating of subcutaneous and dermis will improve
      acne in needed patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
